## What NOT to do

- ❌ Build voice before Phase 1 is solid.
- ❌ Twilio/Telnyx SIP trunks. LiveKit Phone Numbers is faster setup.
- ❌ UK phone number. LiveKit free tier is US numbers; judges dial +1 for free on smartphones.
- ❌ Fork agent logic between voice and text. One planner, two entry points.
- ❌ Skip the filler phrase. Without it, the demo feels broken even when it works.
- ❌ Block voice replies on memory extraction. Always background-task it.
- ❌ Add Deepgram. Use LiveKit's bundled STT.
